Asumsi sesuai setup kamu sebelumnya:
DEV pakai docker-compose.dev.yml dengan project name otomatisin_dev
PROD/LIVE (app.otomatis.in) pakai docker-compose.yml dengan project name otomatisin
Folder kerja: /opt/otomatisin (sesuaikan kalau beda)

A) Rebuild DEV → dev.otomatis.in (aman, cepat, minim sampah)

git pull
docker builder prune -af
docker image prune -af
docker system prune -af --volumes
docker compose -p otomatisin_dev -f docker-compose.dev.yml up -d
docker compose -p otomatisin_dev -f docker-compose.dev.yml build --no-cache postiz-dev
docker compose -p otomatisin_dev -f docker-compose.dev.yml ps
docker compose -p otomatisin_dev -f docker-compose.dev.yml logs --tail 200 -f
curl -sI http://127.0.0.1:4200 | head
curl -sI http://127.0.0.1:3333/auth | head
docker image prune -f

B) Rebuild PROD/LIVE → app.otomatis.in (aman, minim risiko 502/404)
docker compose -p otomatisin -f docker-compose.yml build
docker compose -p otomatisin -f docker-compose.yml up -d
docker compose -p otomatisin -f docker-compose.yml build --no-cache postiz
docker compose -p otomatisin -f docker-compose.yml ps
docker compose -p otomatisin -f docker-compose.yml logs --tail 200 -f
curl -sI https://app.otomatis.in | head -n 20
curl -sI https://api.otomatis.in/auth | head -n 20
curl -sI https://api.otomatis.in/health | head -n 20
docker image prune -f
docker builder prune -f
